    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276190/extras/f38aab0c78aabba90e4638f0144756bc.poster.avif?t=1765891178\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276190/extras/f38aab0c78aabba90e4638f0144756bc.webm?t=1765891178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276190/extras/f38aab0c78aabba90e4638f0144756bc.mp4?t=1765891178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The War of the Worlds: Siberia</strong> is an action/adventure game set in the late XIX century Russian Empire. In an alternate 1896, Earth became the target for a massive Martian invasion. Main characters attempt to save themselves and head for the eastern parts of the country.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276190/extras/aface21d80e7adecf7579119b5bb1e23.avif?t=1765891178\" width=616 height=320 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276190/extras/ea5129f3f428087a29cf4fe6ad8ac50e.avif?t=1765891178\" width=616 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276190/extras/c976a1224e40c78fb66bdc46078161fc.poster.avif?t=1765891178\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276190/extras/c976a1224e40c78fb66bdc46078161fc.webm?t=1765891178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276190/extras/c976a1224e40c78fb66bdc46078161fc.mp4?t=1765891178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terrifying machines from the sky, towering over the horizon, know no defeat. The hero must traverse a path where gigantic tripod machines, their predatory pilots, and the incredible destructive power of Martian technology will constantly threaten his life.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276190/extras/2d6ff557ff52068a00e42f9c05ea27b4.avif?t=1765891178\" width=616 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276190/extras/1f0125885e8fcf30680c906491cf6b17.poster.avif?t=1765891178\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276190/extras/1f0125885e8fcf30680c906491cf6b17.webm?t=1765891178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276190/extras/1f0125885e8fcf30680c906491cf6b17.mp4?t=1765891178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s time to run. The cities that managed to survive are engulfed in looting and violence. Hunger and lawlessness have become abundant fuel for crime wherever humans reside. But far from the megacities, amidst the mountains and taiga, the hope for the salvation of humanity and civilization still lives. Right?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276190/extras/9fcf23fcd2b7f402b329ced389958bfa.avif?t=1765891178\" width=616 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276190/extras/b71f8babdf944ea58d180731f1160150.poster.avif?t=1765891178\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276190/extras/b71f8babdf944ea58d180731f1160150.webm?t=1765891178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276190/extras/b71f8babdf944ea58d180731f1160150.mp4?t=1765891178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The hero must survive and hide from enemies, solve puzzles, and make discoveries. He will have to fight with his fists and use everything he can find. For instance, firearm weapons from that era: revolvers, rifles, muzzle-loading guns, and of course, explosives. The hero will face chases and pursuits, ruthless enemies, and unexpected allies without whom everything would be in vain.</p>",
